<h2>1. What did I do yesterday?</h2>
<div>
  {% for repo, group in yesterday.items() %}
    {% if group.created_prs or group.reviewed_prs or group.created_issues %}
      <p><b>{{ group.repo_shortname }}</b></p>
      <ul>
        {% for pr in group.created_prs %}
          <li>Created PR: <a href='{{ pr.html_url }}'>{{ pr.title }}</a></li>
        {% endfor %}
        {% for pr in group.reviewed_prs %}
          <li>Reviewed PR: <a href='{{ pr.html_url }}'>{{ pr.title }}</a></li>
        {% endfor %}
        {% for issue in group.created_issues %}
          <li>Created Issue: <a href='{{ issue.html_url }}'>{{ issue.title }}</a></li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<h2>2. What do I plan to do today?</h2>
<div id='plans'>
  {% if today %}
    {% for repo, group in today.items() %}
      {% if group.created_prs or group.reviewed_prs or group.created_issues %}
        <p><b>{{ group.repo_shortname }}</b></p>
        <ul>
          {% for pr in group.created_prs %}
            <li><a href='{{ pr.html_url }}'>{{ pr.title }}</a></li>
          {% endfor %}
          {% for pr in group.reviewed_prs %}
            <li><a href='{{ pr.html_url }}'>{{ pr.title }}</a></li>
          {% endfor %}
          {% for issue in group.created_issues %}
            <li><a href='{{ issue.html_url }}'>{{ issue.title }}</a></li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  {% else %}
    <ul>
      <li></li>
    </ul>
  {% endif %}
</div>

<h2>3. What is blocking me from making progress?</h2>
<p>No blocker at the moment</p>
